{
  "texts": [
    "Through a blend of structural and temporal analysis, we discovered prevailing trends and constructed a comprehensive analytical framework.",
    "Our synthesis of findings crystallized into a paradigm, encompassing the quadrants of scenario, modality, task, and method, which collectively shape the nexus of diffusion-based visual art creation.",
    "As we gaze into the future, we propose a novel perspective that intertwines technological and synergistic aspects, characterizing the collaborative ventures between humans and AI in creating visual art.",
    "This perspective beckons a future where AI not only complements human artistry but also actively contributes to the creative process.",
    "However, amidst the rapid technical strides, we are compelled to ponder the implications of AI potentially surpassing human capacity in both understanding and task execution."
  ]
}